trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyProperty" /> que tem como destino o método <see cref="M:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyObject.GetValue(System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyProperty)" />.

trans-unit.source: Allows a custom override of the <see cref="M:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyObject.GetValue(System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyProperty)" /> logic associated with a dependency property that is defined on a dependency object.
trans-unit.target: Permite uma substituição personalizada da lógica <see cref="M:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyObject.GetValue(System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyProperty)" /> associada a uma propriedade de dependência definida em um objeto de dependência.

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.Object" /> that represents the value of the designated <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyProperty" />.
trans-unit.target: Um <see cref="T:System.Object" /> que representa o valor do <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyProperty" /> designado.

trans-unit.source: The implemetation of this delegate can be set on the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.PropertyMetadata.GetValueOverride%2A> property of <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.PropertyMetadata> while calling <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyProperty.Register%2A> or <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyProperty.RegisterAttached%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Implemetation deste delegado pode ser definido na <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.PropertyMetadata.GetValueOverride%2A> propriedade <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.PropertyMetadata> ao chamar <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyProperty.Register%2A> ou <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyProperty.RegisterAttached%2A>.
